data.description: Location, Location, Location. Freshly painted and well maintained bright and sunny 3 bedrooms with newly installed vinyl floor and titled 1 bathroom. Space kitchen with new vinyl floor and appliances. Finished laundry room. Oversized 2 car garage with opener. Near Purdue University, YMCA, bike/walking trail and minutes to express way.Don't forget Hammond's homebound program.
